</p>
<p>international bodies&#8221;.35  She would like to reiterate her concern for Mr. Amro&#8217;s physical 
</p>
<p>and psychological integrity, given the attacks against him and the YAS centre and the 
</p>
<p>seriousness of the allegations, namely that he has received a number of death threats and 
