</p>
<p>on 30 October 2013, which lacks clarity and might be opened up to interpretations that 
</p>
<p>would unduly limit the rights to freedom of association, opinion and expression. She would 
</p>
<p>like to reiterate the concerns that she voiced in a joint press release on 3 December 2013 
</p>
<p>  
</p>
