</p>
<p>                        28/08/2013 
</p>
<p><b>Alleged criminal charges against human rights defenders and alleged 
</b></p>
<p><b>Government campaign against defenders working on Lesbian, Gay, Bisexual, 
</b></p>
<p><b>Transgender and Intersex rights. 
</b></p>
